The paper discusses the use of 2DPCA for face recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel ridge regression model to enhance the generalization ability of extracted features, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of an optimal algorithm, which could fall under the category of information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses image reconstruction, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
